# Content Security Policy
<IfModule mod_headers.c>
    Header set Content-Security-Policy "default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: https:; font-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self' https://*.supabase.co wss://*.supabase.co; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self';"
</IfModule>
